HEADWORD: Geoduck
<hw>Ge"o*duck</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[American Indian
name.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A gigantic clam (<spn>Glycimeris
generosa</spn>) of the Pacific coast of North America, highly valued as
an article of food.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

